\pard\intbl\nowidctlpar\fi-720\li1089\ri339\sa240\qj\expndtw-2 12.5.1\tab\expndtw-1 Broadcom as Controller. Related to the provision of the Broadcom Offerings, Broadcom may process limited Personal Data as a controller in accordance with, and for the purposes defined in, Broadcom\rquote s Privacy \expndtw0 Notice available at https://www.broadcom.com/privacy (or successor\expndtw3  \expndtw0 URL)\expndtw2  \expndtw0 in\expndtw-4  \expndtw0 compliance\expndtw-3  \expndtw0 with\expndtw-4  \expndtw0 applicable data protection laws. Those purposes include: (i) management of Customer relationship; (ii) sales administration; (iii) communications related to technical support, new versions or updates; (iv) marketing of Broadcom Offerings; (v) development of threat intelligence for the purposes of ensuring fraud prevention and network and information security; (vi) development and enhancement of the Broadcom Offerings; and (vii) compliance with applicable laws and regulations.\cell 
\pard\intbl\nowidctlpar\fi-720\li1089\ri92\sa240\qj\expndtw-2\lang3082 12.5.1\tab\expndtw0 Broadcom como Responsable del tratamiento de los datos. En relaci\'f3n con la provisi\'f3n de las Ofertas de Broadcom, Broadcom puede tratar los Datos personales limitados como Responsable del tratamiento de los datos de acuerdo con, y para los fines definidos en, el Aviso de Privacidad de Broadcom disponible \expndtw-1 en: \expndtw0 https://www.broadcom.com/privacy\expndtw-1  en cumplimiento con las leyes de protecci\'f3n de datos aplicables. Dichos fines incluyen: (i) gesti\'f3n de la relaci\'f3n con el Cliente; (ii) administraci\'f3n de ventas; (iii) comunicaciones relacionadas con el soporte t\'e9cnico, nuevas versiones o actualizaciones; (iv) marketing de las Ofertas de Broadcom; (v) desarrollo de inteligencia sobre amenazas con el fin de garantizar la prevenci\'f3n del fraude y la seguridad de la red y de la informaci\'f3n; (vi) desarrollo y mejora de las Ofertas de Broadcom; y (vii) cumplimiento de las leyes y reglamentos aplicables.\expndtw0\cell\row\trowd\trgaph108\trleft-99\trrh126\trpaddl108\trpaddr108\trpaddfl3\trpaddfr3
\cellx4511\cellx9493 
\pard\intbl\nowidctlpar\fi-720\li1089\ri339\sa240\qj\expndtw-2\lang1033 12.5.2\tab\expndtw0 Broadcom as Processor. Where Broadcom processes Personal Data within Customer Data on behalf of Customer, Broadcom\rquote s global Data Processing Addendum (DPA), located \expndtw-2 at https://www.broadcom.com/privacy\cf2  \cf0\expndtw0 (or successor URL), applies. If Customer procures the Broadcom Offering through a Broadcom Partner, the Broadcom Partner shall be responsible for entering into a relevant data processing agreement with Customer.\cell 
\pard\intbl\nowidctlpar\fi-720\li1089\ri92\sa240\qj\expndtw-2\lang3082 12.5.2\tab\expndtw0 Broadcom como Encargado del tratamiento de los datos. Cuando Broadcom trate Datos personales dentro de los Datos del cliente en nombre del Cliente, se aplicar\'e1 el Acuerdo de tratamiento de datos (DPA, por sus siglas en ingl\'e9s) global de Broadcom, ubicado en \expndtw-2 https://www.broadcom.com/privacy\expndtw0  (o URL que la suceda). Si el Cliente adquiere la Oferta de Broadcom a trav\'e9s de un Partner de Broadcom, el Partner de Broadcom ser\'e1 responsable de suscribir un Acuerdo de tratamiento de datos pertinente con el Cliente.\cell\row\trowd\trgaph108\trleft-99\trrh126\trpaddl108\trpaddr108\trpaddfl3\trpaddfr3
\cellx4511\cellx9493 
\pard\intbl\nowidctlpar\fi-567\li669\ri339\sa240\qj\expndtw-2\lang1033 12.6\tab\expndtw0 Assignment. Neither Party shall assign the Agreement or any of its rights or delegate any of its duties under the Agreement, either by operation of law, agreement, or any other process, without the prior written consent of the other Party, except that Broadcom shall have the right to assign the Agreement or any of its rights or delegate any of its duties under the Agreement at any time to any Broadcom Affiliate(s), or to a successor in interest of all or substantially all of the business to which the Agreement relates. Subject to the foregoing, the Agreement will be binding upon, enforceable by, and inure to the benefit of the parties and their respective successors and assigns. Any attempted assignment in violation of this section shall be null and void.\cell 
