\pard\intbl\nowidctlpar\fi-567\li743\ri66\sb74\sa240\qj\expndtw-2 2.1\tab\expndtw0\ldblquote Authorized Use Limitation\rdblquote  or \ldblquote Meter\rdblquote  means the limitation on usage of SaaS as measured by the Billing Metric specified in the Transaction Document.\cell 
\pard\intbl\nowidctlpar\fi-567\li743\sb70\sa240\qj\expndtw-2\lang3082 2.1\tab\expndtw0\ldblquote L\'edmite de uso autorizado\rdblquote  o \ldblquote Medici\'f3n\rdblquote  hacen referencia al l\'edmite de uso del SaaS de acuerdo con la M\'e9trica de facturaci\'f3n especificada en el Documento de transacci\'f3n. \cell\row\trowd\trgaph108\trleft-99\trrh126\trpaddl108\trpaddr108\trpaddfl3\trpaddfr3
